OL,3,CThe price of an underpoured pint:
OL,4,CShort measures cost drinkers #115 a
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FPub-goers hoping for a pint this
OL,8,Fweekend might be left shortchanged -
OL,9,Fafter an investigation found two
OL,10,Fthirds of beer and wine orders were
OL,11,Funder poured.
OL,13,FTrading Standards Officers visited 77
OL,14,Fpubs and bars, and found they were
OL,15,Fserved 96 short measures out of 137
OL,16,Forders.
