OL,3,CThe price of an underpoured pint:
OL,4,CShort measures cost drinkers #115 a
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FThe Chartered Trading Services
OL,8,FInstitute (CTSI) estimates for the
OL,9,Faverage , short measuring equates to a
OL,10,Floss of #1.70 a week - or #88.40 a
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,FFor the that amount jumps to #2.20 a
OL,14,Fweek - or #114.40 a year.
OL,16,FThe largest short measure researchers
OL,17,Ffound was 15% under, on a #3.20 glass
OL,18,Fof wine in Walsall. In Belfast, a
OL,19,F#7.20 glass of wine was found to be
OL,20,F13.4% under poured.
