OL,3,CThe price of an underpoured pint:
OL,4,CShort measures cost drinkers #115 a
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FCTSI Chief Executive, John Herriman,
OL,8,Fsaid the findings paint "a national
OL,9,Fpicture of how widespread short
OL,10,Fmeasuring of alcoholic drinks are."
OL,12,FHe called on the hospitality sector to
OL,13,Fensure consumers were being served
OL,14,Fdrinks that were correctly measured.
OL,16,FLegally, the frothy head on a pint of
OL,17,Fbeer is included in the measure, but
OL,18,Fthe CTSI found that only 23% of the
OL,19,Fpublic think that should be the case.
