OL,7,F(CAMRA) maintains the pint measure
OL,8,Fshould not include the head and
OL,9,Fconsumers should have a right to a
OL,10,F100% liquid pint.
OL,12,FCAMRA national chairman Nik Anton said
OL,13,Fthe CTSI's findings were "concerning".
OL,14,FHe urged consumers served anything
OL,15,Fmore than 5% short to "ask bar staff
OL,16,Ffor an immediate top-up."
